14755  template <class TElemType>
14756  void MetaDataChunkOfElem(const TElemType *elem,
14757  const unsigned long l,
14758  const unsigned long elemEnd,
14759  const unsigned short nElemSimul,
14760  const unsigned short nPadMin,
14761  unsigned long &lEnd,
14762  unsigned short &ind,
14763  unsigned short &llEnd,
14764  unsigned short &NPad) {
14765 
14766  /* Determine the end index for this chunk of elements that must be
14767  treated simulaneously. The elements of this chunk must have the
14768  same standard element in order to make this work. */
14769  const unsigned long lEndMax = min(l+nElemSimul, elemEnd);
14770 
14771  ind = elem[l].indStandardElement;
14772  for(lEnd=l+1; lEnd<lEndMax; ++lEnd) {
14773  if(elem[lEnd].indStandardElement != ind) break;
14774  }
14775 
14776  /* Store the number of elements that are treated simultaneously in this chunk
14777  in llEnd and determine the padded N value in the gemm computations. */
14778  llEnd = lEnd - l;
14779  NPad = llEnd*nVar;
14780  if( NPad%nPadMin ) NPad += nPadMin - (NPad%nPadMin);
14781  }
14782 };
